                        <interp inst="t18461026-name-710" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS HAZELDINE</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable D</hi> 104.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted 6th Jan.</hi>, 1846, <hi rend="italic">and confined six months</hi>)—the prisoner is the person—he is a very bad character, and goes about with thieves.</p>
